```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[前端操作<br/>暂停/恢复/取消] --> B[gRPC API<br/>PauseTask/ResumeTask/CancelTask]

    B --> C[Temporal Client]
    C --> D[发送 Workflow Signal<br/>pause_v1/resume_v1/cancel_v1]

    D --> E[父 Workflow<br/>SignalHandler]

    E --> F[更新控制状态<br/>paused/cancelled]
    E --> G[传播信号到子 Workflow]

    G --> H[子 Workflow<br/>SignalHandler]
    H --> I[子 Workflow 控制状态更新]

    F --> J[父 Workflow 到达 CheckPausePoint]
    I --> K[子 Workflow 到达 CheckPausePoint]

    J --> L{当前状态}
    K --> M{当前状态}

    L -->|paused| N[workflow.Await 阻塞]
    L -->|cancelled| O[返回取消错误]
    L -->|normal| P[继续执行]

    M -->|paused| Q[workflow.Await 阻塞]
    M -->|cancelled| R[返回取消错误]
    M -->|normal| S[继续执行]

    N --> T[resume_v1 到达后继续]
    Q --> U[resume_v1 到达后继续]

    E --> V[SSE 事件<br/>workflow.pausing/paused/resumed]
    H --> V
    V --> W[前端实时展示状态]
```

